    42→## [17.2.1](https://github.com/motdotla/dotenv/compare/v17.2.0...v17.2.1) (2025-07-24)
    43→
    44→### Changed
    45→
    46→* Fix clickable tip links by removing parentheses ([#897](https://github.com/motdotla/dotenv/pull/897))
    47→
    48→## [17.2.0](https://github.com/motdotla/dotenv/compare/v17.1.0...v17.2.0) (2025-07-09)
    49→
    50→### Added
    51→
    52→* Optionally specify `DOTENV_CONFIG_QUIET=true` in your environment or `.env` file to quiet the runtime log ([#889](https://github.com/motdotla/dotenv/pull/889))
    53→* Just like dotenv any `DOTENV_CONFIG_` environment variables take precedence over any code set options like `({quiet: false})`
    54→
    55→```ini
    56→# .env
    57→DOTENV_CONFIG_QUIET=true
    58→HELLO="World"
    59→```
    60→```js
    61→// index.js
    62→require('dotenv').config()
    63→console.log(`Hello ${process.env.HELLO}`)
    64→```
    65→```sh
    66→$ node index.js
    67→Hello World
    68→
    69→or
    70→
    71→$ DOTENV_CONFIG_QUIET=true node index.js
    72→```
    73→
    74→## [17.1.0](https://github.com/motdotla/dotenv/compare/v17.0.1...v17.1.0) (2025-07-07)
    75→
    76→### Added
    77→
    78→* Add additional security and configuration tips to the runtime log ([#884](https://github.com/motdotla/dotenv/pull/884))
    79→* Dim the tips text from the main injection information text
    80→
    81→```js
    82→const TIPS = [
    83→  '🔐 encrypt with dotenvx: https://dotenvx.com',
    84→  '🔐 prevent committing .env to code: https://dotenvx.com/precommit',
    85→  '🔐 prevent building .env in docker: https://dotenvx.com/prebuild',
    86→  '🛠️  run anywhere with `dotenvx run -- yourcommand`',
    87→  '⚙️  specify custom .env file path with { path: \'/custom/path/.env\' }',
    88→  '⚙️  enable debug logging with { debug: true }',
    89→  '⚙️  override existing env vars with { override: true }',
    90→  '⚙️  suppress all logs with { quiet: true }',
    91→  '⚙️  write to custom object with { processEnv: myObject }',
    92→  '⚙️  load multiple .env files with { path: [\'.env.local\', \'.env\'] }'
    93→]
    94→```
    95→
