   293→## [15.0.0](https://github.com/motdotla/dotenv/compare/v14.3.2...v15.0.0) (2022-01-31)
   294→
   295→`v15.0.0` is a major new release with some important breaking changes.
   296→
   297→### Added
   298→
   299→- _Breaking:_ Multiline parsing support (just works. no need for the flag.)
   300→
   301→### Changed
   302→
   303→- _Breaking:_ `#` marks the beginning of a comment (UNLESS the value is wrapped in quotes. Please update your `.env` files to wrap in quotes any values containing `#`. For example: `SECRET_HASH="something-with-a-#-hash"`).
   304→
   307→### Removed
   308→
   309→- _Breaking:_ Remove multiline option (just works out of the box now. no need for the flag.)
   310→
